headline: Could ICE’s (ICE) Expanding ETF Index Licensing Hint at a Broader Competitive Edge?
summary: Global X Investments Canada announced it has licensed Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) indices to launch four BetaPro leveraged and inverse ETFs, offering very large daily exposures to the ICE U.S. Treasury 20+ Year Bond Index and NYSE Semiconductor Index. This development underscores ICE's influence in benchmark administration, with its indices already used for over US$2 trillion in assets, reflecting widespread market adoption and relevance.
